    <template>
        <think><set name="welcome">true</set></think>
        Welcome to :rabbit: *APIbunny* game. <br/>
        It's an adventure game around the theme of Easter. Explore around, solve puzzles to get clues and find the exit password. <br />
        If you get lost tweet at &lt;https://twitter.com/picsoung | @picsoung&gt; or  &lt;https://twitter.com/3scale | @3scale&gt; and we will help you out <br />
        Follow the conversation on &lt;https://twitter.com/hashtag/apibunny | Twitter&gt; <br />
        :old_key: indicates that there is a puzzle to solve in this room, just type your answer, and the APIbunny will let you know if it's right or not <br />
        :runner: type `go [direction]` to move around<br />
        To get started say `start` <br />
        Enjoy!
        :rabbit: :chocolate_bar: :rabbit: :chocolate_bar: :rabbit: :chocolate_bar: :rabbit: :chocolate_bar: :rabbit: :chocolate_bar: :rabbit: :chocolate_bar: :rabbit: :chocolate_bar:
